        Social Proof for House Cleaners
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Homeowners need to trust someone before they hand over a key to their house. That trust comes from what other clients say about you. SocialProof helps you collect client testimonials automatically and display them on your site so new customers can see you're reliable, thorough, and trustworthy — before they ever call.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why trust is the #1 selling point for house cleaners</h2>
      <p>Clients aren't just paying for clean floors — they're letting you into their private space, often when they're not home. Price matters, but trust matters more. A new client who can see that 10 other homeowners rave about you will book faster and with less friction than one staring at a blank website.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Most cleaning services win or lose on Nextdoor, Facebook groups, and word of mouth. SocialProof brings that word-of-mouth onto your own website where you control the presentation.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What client reviews look like for cleaning services</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
