        <li><strong>Thoroughness:</strong> "Noticed things we didn't even know needed cleaning. Baseboards, vents, everything."</li>
        <li><strong>Trust:</strong> "We leave a key for her and never think twice about it. Total peace of mind."</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "Texts when she's on her way and when she's done. So easy to work with."</li>
        <li><strong>Results:</strong> "House smells incredible after every visit. My family noticed the difference immediately."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your cleaning business</h2>
