      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Best time to ask: right after a great clean</h2>
      <p>Don't wait weeks — ask when the client is still thrilled. Right after you finish a particularly good job, shoot them a quick text: "Hope everything looks great! If you have a moment, I'd love a quick review: [link]" That's it. Two sentences and a link.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you one permanent link you can save in your phone and drop into any message. Simple, fast, effective.</p>

